entry.title: ShipBit/slickgpt
entry.summary: SlickGPT is a light-weight "use-your-own-API-key" ChatGPT client written in Svelte. It offers GPT-4 integration, a userless share feature and other superpowers.

entry.title: bennymi/svhighlight
entry.summary: A code syntax highlighter for Svelte using highlight.js, with line blur and highligthing and focus buttons. The component can be easily customized with Tailwind CSS.
